  "powergrid.ponder.electromagnet.text_3": "当物品在传送带上提供时...",
  "powergrid.ponder.electromagnet.text_4": "电磁铁将自动保持并处理它们",
  "powergrid.ponder.fuse.header": "保护您的设备",
